mAttachmentContainer

protected IAeAttachmentContainer mAttachmentContainer
The optional associated attachments for all variable types. Note that this container calways has the correct attachment information for the variable even when the variable is of type message. For message type variables the getMessageData method will make right the attachment information returned with the message.
